{NORTH has 20 points, counting one extra for the fifth Diamond. Just right to open 2NT.

SOUTH has 6 points, just enough to bid 3NT. 
(20 + 6 = 26) (21 + 6 = 27)}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "W"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
[Deal "W:QT3.KT6.A94.T752 6.QJ742.632.A963 KJ92.A98.QT8.KQJ A8754.53.KJ75.84"]
